    <item>
      <title>主权评级下调后穆迪下调中国银行业展望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/moody-s-cuts-outlook-on-chinese-banks-after-sovereign-downgrade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[出于对债务水平的担忧，穆迪投资者服务公司将八家中国银行的前景从稳定下调至负面。一天前，穆迪投资者服务公司公布了对中国主权债券的看跌立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/moody-s-cuts-outlook-on-chinese-banks-after-sovereign-downgrade</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 11:48:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万达亿万富翁创始人在债务压力增大时出售电影部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/wanda-s-billionaire-founder-sells-film-unit-as-debt-pressure-builds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大连万达集团有限公司创始人王健林正计划出售该公司剩余的电影部门，因为这家陷入困境的中国企业集团面临着越来越大的债务偿还压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/wanda-s-billionaire-founder-sells-film-unit-as-debt-pressure-builds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 07:52:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
